1 AN ACT
2 RELATING TO PUBLIC WORKS; REQUIRING CONTRIBUTIONS TO
3 APPRENTICE AND TRAINING PROGRAMS OR TO THE PUBLIC WORKS
4 APPRENTICE AND TRAINING FUND FOR PUBLIC WORKS CONSTRUCTION
